description:
On today’s show, Emily is joined by sexological bodyworker Dolly Josette to talk about how people can really get reconnected to their body and their sexual energy.

They discuss what the heck vulva-mapping is and how can it help you and your partner get acquainted with your body, how you can work together to have the most pleasurable experiences possible, and why masturbation is the motivation. Plus, did you know – you can have an EARgasm?!
